description: Welcome to 199 West Eighth Street. This upper level home lives large with no wasted space and is nearly 1050 sqft with 2 oversized bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, plus a large open living layout perfect for entertaining guests. The kitchen has an oversized breakfast bar with Quartz countertops, stainless appliances, wood cabinetry and under cabinet lighting.  The primary bedroom suite has 2 custom closets, fantastic light, and a spacious ensuite bath with double vanity sinks and marble step-in shower. The guest bedroom is also spacious and has excellent storage and light.  Other amenities include hardwood floors throughout, a gas fireplace, central air conditioning, recessed lightening, and low condo fees.  1 garage parking space is included. This home is just steps to the MBTA/Red line, shops, restaurants, & a Commuters dream, just min to 93/90
